| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2616 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: f0129354-ba6d-5417-9e06-cb4ad5c3acbb"
